and by that, there's

00:00:53.580 --> 00:00:55.920
different things
in this space that

00:00:55.920 --> 00:00:59.380
are situated to how you
like to learn and study.

00:00:59.380 --> 00:01:01.260
So we have a standing
table if that's

00:01:01.260 --> 00:01:03.960
your preferred way of writing.

00:01:03.960 --> 00:01:05.062
We have stress balls.

00:01:05.062 --> 00:01:07.020
We have coloring books
for, like, when you just

00:01:07.020 --> 00:01:08.017
need to de-stress.

00:01:08.017 --> 00:01:09.600
And I also think
it's really important

00:01:09.600 --> 00:01:12.240
that there's a lot
of vivid colors

00:01:12.240 --> 00:01:13.890
that really keep
you excited to be

00:01:13.890 --> 00:01:15.765
in the space and, like,
awake and productive.

